==Useful Info==
'''Cherubim''' are flying holy beings with a 6-tile halo [[aura]]. Although less dangerous than [[angel]]s or [[daeva]]s, they tend to wield decent weapons of [[flaming]] or [[holy wrath]] and fire [[longbow]]s at you. They are rare, only appearing in the [[Abyss]] and holy-themed [[Pandemonium]] and [[Ziggurat]] floors.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*Like [[orc knight]]s, cherubim have a [[Battlecry]] ability that allows them to empower monsters around them, causing these allies to deal +30% damage.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.28]], cherubim could [[see invisible]].
